Excalibur usually plays 4.Nc3... so this was a surprise. White decides on pushing the queen ahead. 4...Ne7 is forced since 4...Be7? leads to 5.Qxg7... +/-  and 4...Qe7 allows 5.Qxc7... +/-
White's play is active, and pressurises my own development. However, with calm moves, I can react sufficiently.
